Package com.csse3200.game.gamestate

Class GameState

java.lang.Object
com.csse3200.game.gamestate.GameState
public class GameState extends Object
A data struct that contains other data structs to be saved to JSONs by SaveHandler. Fields MUST be static. Not to be kept between playthroughs.
